        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Unexpected Findings After 43 Hours Testing</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-black">What nobody tells accounting firms about websites</p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-slate-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Service clarity visible: 5x more qualified inquiries</p>
