            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Client testimonials visible: 4x more trust</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Added client testimonials with results prominently. Month 1: 4x higher inquiry rate. Results = you deliver = trust = hire you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-slate-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Free resources visible: 67% more leads</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Added tax checklist, financial planning guides. Month 1: 67% more email signups. Value upfront = you know your stuff = hire you.</p>
