            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Mobile firm site: 71% search on phones</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Business owners = search on phone. Non-responsive = skip this firm. Mobile-optimized = they engage. Accounting = mobile.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
